{
  "stem": "15686.4",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, we were at this little home for small children in Limoges.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In Vichy, France, unoccupied France.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And because all the children there were real small, the people that were running this place thought we'd be happier in a place where there were children of our age, of course.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the organization-- the [?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "OSE ?] I referred to earlier, had several homes not far from Limoges.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we were sent to a place called Le Chateau de Chabannes about 100 miles from Limoges-- 100 miles northeast, but still within Vichy, France, unoccupied France.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We arrived there, and there were about 100 children there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Half of them were German or Austrian refugee children.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "The other half were French Jewish children.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It was a nice place.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It was [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] very countrified, in the middle of nowhere, in a very rural, backward part of France.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Way off the beaten tourist paths.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Even today, nobody ever goes there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] We were in this little village.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And basically, we lived off-- off the land.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "We would go out and go to the local farmers, and try to buy vegetables, and fruit, and whatever meat we could, or chickens, or what have you.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] try to keep ourselves supplied as much as we could.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Where the money came from at that point, we didn't know.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And we didn't care, either.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "We were just glad to have a place to stay.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I mean, we didn't care-- it wasn't being callous.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But we just weren't inquisitive.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we had learned, you know, that asking too many questions cannot-- is sometimes very unhealthy during wartime, so.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The place was very [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] nice, because we were finally among children our own age.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
